@startuml

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title FTP: control connection vs data connection

actor Client
node "FTP Server" as S

Client -> S : TCP 21 (control)\nUSER/PASS, PWD, LIST, RETR/STOR
note right of S
Long-lived connection
commands + responses
end note

Client -> S : TCP (data)\nLIST / RETR / STOR
note right of S
Separate connection
data transfer only
end note

@enduml
